headline: Jacobs Appointed Engineering, Procurement and Construction Management Lead for Hut 8 AI Data Center
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by Hut 8 (NASDAQ: HUT), an energy infrastructure platform, to deliver Engineering, Procurement and Construction Management (EPCM) services for its River Bend data center in Louisiana.
